{"tid":679123,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後係咪發錢寒？叫佢幫手下整小小既都Charge返我朋友錢，有無攪錯！","createTime":"2018-05-26T15:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T05:09:46.000Z","uid":19334,"like":12,"dislike":275,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a101874d3b7a18be37f8a0d956e43fc75718ac","tid":679123,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"話說我有個朋友要影擺酒結婚相，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢話出面搵人影好貴，一時又臨時臨急找到人影etc......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我印象中記得公司有隻90後係freelance photographer，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我咪叫佢幫幫手影擺酒結婚相，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁過程都係好短，由朝早7:26佈置花車，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟手接新娘去到行紅地毯，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後佢留到夜晚擺酒12:43送親友後先走，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自問我朋友過程中好都有禮貌(非要求多多的西客)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後臨走都有比利是佢+叫佢自己飛的走（比左封$50利是佢），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁今日我就問佢拎相啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢竟然夠膽死問我拎錢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬果日已經無叫你比人情啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢竟然話收我300/Hour，total埋單$4,500.00，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痴撚線，發錢寒成咁！早知我自己渣Iphone去影好過啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb57ad1d2d9473cd8e7aaed166642a4c6acae24b","tid":679123,"uid":180418,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"你真膠定假膠ar <img sr